><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity: 1; transform: none; transition: opacity 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1), transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1);\"><span class=\"section-number\">N°004</span></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity: 1; transform: none; transition: opacity 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) 0.08s, transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) 0.08s;\"><h1 class=\"display-page text-espresso mt-4 mb-8\">A deliberate real-estate practice.</h1></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity: 1; transform: none; transition: opacity 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) 0.16s, transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) 0.16s;\"><p class=\"body-copy text-warm-grey max-w-xl\">Casa Aurelia is not a brokerage operating at scale. We are a small, intentional practice that works with a limited number of clients and properties at any given time.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"relative w-full h-[50vh] md:h-[60vh] lg:h-[70vh] overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 md:pl-[12vw]\"><img alt=\"A bright, thoughtfully arranged interior space with natural materials and clean lines\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fabout-studio.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fabout-studio.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fabout-studio.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fabout-studio.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fabout-studio.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fabout-studio.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fabout-studio.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fabout-studio.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fabout-studio.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"></div></section><section class=\"py-20 md:py-28 lg:py-36\"><div class=\"container-site\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-16 items-center\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-7\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px);transition:opacity 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0s, transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0s\"><span class=\"section-number\">Philosophy</span></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px);transition:opacity 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0.08s, transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0.08s\"><p class=\"display-section text-espresso mt-6 leading-[1.05]\">Fewer listings. More attention. Clear advice. Straightforward communication.</p></div></div><div class=\"lg:col-span-5\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity: 1; transform: none; transition: opacity 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) 0.16s, transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) 0.16s;\"><div class=\"relative aspect-[4/5] overflow-hidden\"><img alt=\"Interior detail showing natural materials and considered design\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 40vw\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fabout-studio.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fabout-studio.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fabout-studio.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fabout-studio.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fabout-studio.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fabout-studio.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fabout-studio.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fabout-studio.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fabout-studio.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fabout-studio.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fabout-studio.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"></div></div></div></div></div></section><hr class=\"editorial-rule mx-auto max-w-[1600px]\"><section class=\"py-20 md:py-28 lg:py-36\"><div class=\"container-editorial\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px);transition:opacity 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0s, transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0s\"><span class=\"section-number\">What We Do</span></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px);transition:opacity 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0.08s, transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0.08s\"><h2 class=\"display-section text-espresso mt-4 mb-12\">Three things, done carefully.</h2></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><div class=\"py-6 border-b border-espresso/8 transition-all duration-500\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-6\"><span class=\"label-micro shrink-0 w-6 transition-colors duration-500 text-espresso/20\">01</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"h-px transition-all duration-700 ease-out mb-4 w-0 bg-cobalt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><h3 class=\"font-display text-lg md:text-xl text-espresso mb-2\">Curate residential properties</h3><p class=\"body-copy text-warm-grey max-w-md transition-all duration-500 overflow-hidden max-h-0 opacity-0 mt-0\" style=\"transition-property:max-height, opacity;transition-timing-function:cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1);transition-duration:0.5s\">We visit, photograph, and evaluate every property before it appears on our platform. Selection is based on design quality, location, and lasting value — not volume.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"py-6 border-b border-espresso/8 transition-all duration-500\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-6\"><span class=\"label-micro shrink-0 w-6 transition-colors duration-500 text-espresso/20\">02</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"h-px transition-all duration-700 ease-out mb-4 w-0 bg-cobalt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><h3 class=\"font-display text-lg md:text-xl text-espresso mb-2\">Help owners sell thoughtfully</h3><p class=\"body-copy text-warm-grey max-w-md transition-all duration-500 overflow-hidden max-h-0 opacity-0 mt-0\" style=\"transition-property:max-height, opacity;transition-timing-function:cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1);transition-duration:0.5s\">We work with sellers to present their property accurately and attract qualified buyers. From pricing to photography to closing, the process is structured and transparent.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"py-6 border-b border-espresso/8 transition-all duration-500\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-6\"><span class=\"label-micro shrink-0 w-6 transition-colors duration-500 text-espresso/20\">03</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"h-px transition-all duration-700 ease-out mb-4 w-0 bg-cobalt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><h3 class=\"font-display text-lg md:text-xl text-espresso mb-2\">Provide private advice</h3><p class=\"body-copy text-warm-grey max-w-md transition-all duration-500 overflow-hidden max-h-0 opacity-0 mt-0\" style=\"transition-property:max-height, opacity;transition-timing-function:cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1);transition-duration:0.5s\">Whether you are buying your first premium property or navigating a complex sale, we offer guidance tailored to your situation — not a generic script.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><hr class=\"editorial-rule mx-auto max-w-[1600px]\"><section class=\"py-20 md:py-28 lg:py-36\"><div class=\"container-editorial\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px);transition:opacity 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0s, transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0s\"><span class=\"section-number\">Selection</span></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px);transition:opacity 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0.08s, transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0.08s\"><h2 class=\"heading-property text-espresso mt-4 mb-12\">How properties make it onto the platform</h2></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px);transition:opacity 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0.16s, transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0.16s\"><p class=\"body-copy text-warm-grey mb-16\">Every listing begins with a visit. Properties that don't meet our standards simply don't get listed.</p></div><div class=\"relative\"><div class=\"absolute left-[23px] md:left-[31px] top-0 bottom-0 w-px bg-espresso/10\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><ol class=\"space-y-12 md:space-y-16\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px);transition:opacity 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0s, transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0s\"><li class=\"relative pl-14 md:pl-20\"><div class=\"absolute left-[18px] md:left-[26px] top-1.5 w-[11px] h-[11px] rounded-full border-2 border-espresso/30 bg-ivory\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><span class=\"label-micro text-warm-grey\">01</span><h3 class=\"font-display text-xl md:text-2xl text-espresso mt-1 mb-2\">Visit</h3><p class=\"body-copy text-warm-grey max-w-md\">We walk through the property ourselves. No relying on third-party photos or descriptions.</p></li></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px);transition:opacity 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0.06s, transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0.06s\"><li class=\"relative pl-14 md:pl-20\"><div class=\"absolute left-[18px] md:left-[26px] top-1.5 w-[11px] h-[11px] rounded-full border-2 border-espresso/30 bg-ivory\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><span class=\"label-micro text-warm-grey\">02</span><h3 class=\"font-display text-xl md:text-2xl text-espresso mt-1 mb-2\">Assess</h3><p class=\"body-copy text-warm-grey max-w-md\">Design quality, location merit, and structural integrity are evaluated against clear criteria.</p></li></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px);transition:opacity 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0.12s, transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0.12s\"><li class=\"relative pl-14 md:pl-20\"><div class=\"absolute left-[18px] md:left-[26px] top-1.5 w-[11px] h-[11px] rounded-full border-2 border-espresso/30 bg-ivory\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><span class=\"label-micro text-warm-grey\">03</span><h3 class=\"font-display text-xl md:text-2xl text-espresso mt-1 mb-2\">Verify</h3><p class=\"body-copy text-warm-grey max-w-md\">Legal status, documentation, and ownership are checked before we proceed.</p></li></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px);transition:opacity 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0.18s, transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0.18s\"><li class=\"relative pl-14 md:pl-20\"><div class=\"absolute left-[18px] md:left-[26px] top-1.5 w-[11px] h-[11px] rounded-full border-2 border-espresso/30 bg-ivory\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><span class=\"label-micro text-warm-grey\">04</span><h3 class=\"font-display text-xl md:text-2xl text-espresso mt-1 mb-2\">Present</h3><p class=\"body-copy text-warm-grey max-w-md\">Professional photography and honest copywriting — no inflated claims.</p></li></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px);transition:opacity 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0.24s, transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0.24s\"><li class=\"relative pl-14 md:pl-20\"><div class=\"absolute left-[18px] md:left-[26px] top-1.5 w-[11px] h-[11px] rounded-full border-2 border-espresso/30 bg-ivory\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><span class=\"label-micro text-warm-grey\">05</span><h3 class=\"font-display text-xl md:text-2xl text-espresso mt-1 mb-2\">Introduce</h3><p class=\"body-copy text-warm-grey max-w-md\">The property is presented to buyers who match its profile. Quietly, deliberately.</p></li></div></ol></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 md:py-28 lg:py-36 bg-espresso\"><div class=\"container-editorial\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px);transition:opacity 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0s, transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0s\"><span class=\"section-number text-warm-grey\">Approach</span></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px);transition:opacity 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0.08s, transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0.08s\"><p class=\"display-section text-ivory mt-6 leading-[1.05]\">Direct. Transparent. Unhurried.</p></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px);transition:opacity 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0.16s, transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0.16s\"><p class=\"body-copy-light mt-8 max-w-lg\">There are no high-pressure tactics here. If a property isn't right for you, we'll say so. If we think your expectations need recalibrating, we'll have that conversation honestly. Our job is to help you make a good decision — not to close a deal at any cost.</p></div></div></section><hr class=\"editorial-rule mx-auto max-w-[1600px]\"><section class=\"py-20 md:py-28 lg:py-36\"><div class=\"container-site\"><div class=\"container-editorial\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px);transition:opacity 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0s, transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0s\"><span class=\"section-number\">Regions</span></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px);transition:opacity 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0.08s, transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0.08s\"><h2 class=\"heading-property text-espresso mt-4 mb-12\">Where we work</h2></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px);transition:opacity 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0.16s, transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0.16s\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-x-8 gap-y-3 md:gap-x-12 md:gap-y-4\"><a class=\"font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-espresso/20 hover:text-espresso transition-colors duration-300 cursor-view\" style=\"transition-delay:0ms\" href=\"/properties?city=Goa\" data-cursor-bound=\"true\">Goa</a><a class=\"font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:te